{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2018-02-09-marking-http-pages-as-not-secure","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"kevinhakanson.com","author":"Kevin Hakanson"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"68cc1cfd-0766-593f-a78c-71986e8aaed6","excerpt":"Chromium Blog: A secure web is here to stay put a deadline for marking HTTP as “Not Secure”: Beginning in July 2018 with the release of Chrome 68, Chrome will…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://blog.chromium.org/2018/02/a-secure-web-is-here-to-stay.html\">Chromium Blog: A secure web is here to stay</a> put a deadline for marking HTTP as “Not Secure”:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Beginning in July 2018 with the release of Chrome 68, Chrome will mark all HTTP sites as “not secure”.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>What if you want that behavior today?  Below are the configurations to change along with what it looks like accessing the intentionally “not secure” <a href=\"http://neverssl.com/\">http://neverssl.com/</a>.</p>\n<p>In Chrome go to <code class=\"language-text\">chrome://flags</code> and search for <code class=\"language-text\">mark-non-secure-as</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a7c028d84673a82740d81dfb2f46f14/6f2d1/pastedImage_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.715481171548117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAeUlEQVQI12XMMQ7CIBhA4V7duHkKF528gvEQXkGgP6QFTIEo6LNldXh52zeY+YVSGhHBmJGHUoi1aK1JKdFa+6vWBnx55g9qemPmip4qLjYGN4UVMtgVsdYRQiDGiPe+g1s5Z0op/VvLkjp4uyd2J+FwsezPwvHq+QE8AZY9e0uczwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Chrome settings\"\n        title=\"Chrome settings\"\n        src=\"/static/0a7c028d84673a82740d81dfb2f46f14/799d3/pastedImage_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0a7c028d84673a82740d81dfb2f46f14/00d96/pastedImage_4.png 148w,\n/static/0a7c028d84673a82740d81dfb2f46f14/0b23c/pastedImage_4.png 295w,\n/static/0a7c028d84673a82740d81dfb2f46f14/799d3/pastedImage_4.png 590w,\n/static/0a7c028d84673a82740d81dfb2f46f14/6f2d1/pastedImage_4.png 717w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 337px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/634a76ae560682624647c1146f064423/a4aa2/pastedImage_6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.059347181008896%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Chrome &quot;Not Secure&quot;\"\n        title=\"Chrome &quot;Not Secure&quot;\"\n        src=\"/static/634a76ae560682624647c1146f064423/a4aa2/pastedImage_6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/634a76ae560682624647c1146f064423/00d96/pastedImage_6.png 148w,\n/static/634a76ae560682624647c1146f064423/0b23c/pastedImage_6.png 295w,\n/static/634a76ae560682624647c1146f064423/a4aa2/pastedImage_6.png 337w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 337px) 100vw, 337px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolu